  "title": "DIGITAL MARKETING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an DIGITAL MARKETING EXECUTIVE to join our Marketing team in Singapore. This role requires a creative individual, with excellent writing skills, and a strong understanding of <strong>Generative Artificial Intelligence (Gen-AI)</strong>. The ability to learn quickly, adapt new skills, and work independently are critical.</p><p>Able to provide beneficial solutions for these 2 main factors - Sales & Marketing and Customer Engagement.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Sales & Marketing:</strong></u></p><p>- Develop unique marketing content via emails, social media posts, etc. For Individual campaign strategies.</p><p>- Shorten marketing preparation processes, harness Gen-AI to develop engaging contents.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Customer Engagement:</strong></u></p><p>- Providing different solutions to clients for them to engage customers using Gen-AI powered chat boxes, searching for information, personalised recommendations or reservations.</p><p>- The proposed solutions will free up manpower to optimize efficiency & customer experience.</p><p>- Research and analyse potential partner relationships for the product and generate ideas to grow market share, improve customer experience and drive growth.</p><p>- Drive market research studies to explore new technology and oversee development of business proposals for new opportunities.</p><p>- Support product positioning and customer demand, and guide product development from conception to launch.</p><p>- Evaluate product functionalities and performance and propose enhancements to products based on market feedback.<br /></p><p><u>Requirements:</u></p><p>- Possess a Bachelor's Degree (preferably in Gen-AI or related discipline).</p><p>- Minimum 2 years of relevant work experience in Gen-AI environment (in Sales or in Operations).</p><p>- Able to do presentation to all corporate levels with confidence.</p><p>- Able to start work immediately.</p><p><strong>--------------------</strong></p><p><strong>Whatsapp text ONLY +65 82250145</strong></p><p><strong>--------------------</strong></p>",
